OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FFunding pledge for disabled
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fpeople's homes shelved     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government has quietly dropped a   
OL,6, commitment to increase the amount of   
OL,7, money that disabled people in England  
OL,8, can claim to adapt their homes.        
OL,10,FThe Disabled Facilities Grant is used  
OL,11,Fto fund alterations aimed at easing    
OL,12,Fliving at home, such as installing     
OL,13,Fwet-rooms or stairlifts.               
OL,15,FThe maximum amount a person is entitled
OL,16,Fto claim has been capped at #30,000    
OL,17,Fsince 2008.                            
OL,19,FBut in real terms, that means it's now 
OL,20,Fworth around a third less.             
